.0, \"rank\": 1.4195353203961567e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This expands the acceptance of UPI in Paris after a successful launch at the iconic Eiffel Tower,\\\" according to an Indian Embassy statement quoted by ANI.\", \"from\": 540, \"to\": 694, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 571, \"end\": 574, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Unified_Payments_Interface\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.541553663515817e-23, \"text\": \"UPI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Unified_Payments_Interface\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Unified_Payments_Interface\"}, {\"begin\": 578, \"end\": 583, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4195353203961567e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 690, \"end\": 693, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_News_International\", \"score\": 0.9993711573361662, \"rank\": 0.0006048618711106187, \"text\": \"ANI\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_News_International\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_News_International\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Monaco Jawed Ashraf, Indian Ambassador to France and Principality of Monaco, launched UPI by using it live at the store in the presence of Nicolas Houze, CEO of Galeries Lafayette, and Alain Lacour, Chairman of Lyra Group.\", \"from\": 696, \"to\": 918, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 696, \"end\": 702, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Monaco\", \"score\": 0.999997844941666, \"rank\": 2.1508032588450085e-06, \"text\": \"Monaco\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Monaco\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Monaco\"}, {\"begin\": 709