tion_of_India\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The introduction of UPI at Galeries Lafayette is expected to draw hordes of Indian visitors.\", \"from\": 1284, \"to\": 1376, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1304, \"end\": 1307, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Unified_Payments_Interface\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.541553663515817e-23, \"text\": \"UPI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Unified_Payments_Interface\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Unified_Payments_Interface\"}, {\"begin\": 1360, \"end\": 1366, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\", \"score\": 0.88297486544521, \"rank\": 0.13253453506444354, \"text\": \"Indian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Ambassador recalled the first international launch of UPI in Singapore in 2018.. and expressed satisfaction at the international journey of UPI,\\\" ANI reported.\", \"from\": 1380, \"to\": 1540, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1435, \"end\": 1438, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Unified_Payments_Interface\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.541553663515817e-23, \"text\": \"UPI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Unified_Payments_Interface\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Unified_Payments_Interface\"}, {\"begin\": 1442, \"end\": 1451, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\", \"score\": 0.9999223403067521, \"rank\": 7.757136811680232e-05, \"text\": \"Singapore\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\"}, {\"begin\": 1521, \"end\": 1524, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Unified_Payments_Interface\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.541553663515817e-23, \"text\": \"UPI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Unified_Payments_Interface\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/reso